YOU TWO, STAY HERE.

39
00:16:24,065 --> 00:16:26,067
APPLE BUTTER,
PLEASE, MISS MARY.

40
00:17:28,629 --> 00:17:30,631
GOOD EVENING,
THOMAS.

41
00:18:00,161 --> 00:18:01,162
( Sid chuckles )

