48
00:20:47,828 --> 00:20:49,330
THAT'S ALL.

49
00:20:51,832 --> 00:20:53,334
WATCH YOU DON'T
SLOP NONE.

50
00:21:09,850 --> 00:21:11,852
LOOK AT HIM HAVIN'
ALL THAT FUN.

51
00:21:15,356 --> 00:21:16,857
I DONE ATE SOME,
BUT IT'S HALF GOOD.

52
00:21:21,362 --> 00:21:23,864
HEY, WATCH
YOU DON'T SLOP ANY.

53
00:22:57,958 --> 00:23:00,961
♪♪ WHEN YOUR SHOULDER'S
TO THE WHEEL ♪♪

54
00:24:00,020 --> 00:24:02,523
( screaming )

55
00:24:42,062 --> 00:24:45,065
( screaming
and laughing )

56
00:24:57,578 --> 00:25:00,581
( rattle )

57
00:25:57,971 --> 00:26:00,974
