ONLY OLD HOSS KNOWS THAT.
( laughs )

66
00:29:06,159 --> 00:29:07,160
JUST A MINUTE, BOY.

67
00:29:08,662 --> 00:29:10,664
( whistles )

68
00:29:18,672 --> 00:29:21,675
THERE YOU ARE.
( laughs )

69
00:30:13,226 --> 00:30:15,729
♪♪ THERE AIN'T
NO FIGHTIN' FATE ♪♪

70
00:31:05,779 --> 00:31:08,281
♪♪ THERE' AIN'T NO FIGHTIN' FATE ♪♪

71
00:31:58,832 --> 00:32:00,333
( laughter )

72
00:32:03,336 --> 00:32:05,839
THERE IT IS.
( all laugh )

73
00:32:20,854 --> 00:32:22,355
( Tom and Huck laugh )

74
00:32:50,884 --> 00:32:58,892
♪♪ THERE AIN'T
NO FIGHTIN' FATE ♪♪

75
00:33:00,393 --> 00:33:02,395
( Tom and Huck laugh )

76
00:33:45,438 --> 00:33:46,439
AUNT POLLY!

77
00:33:52,445 --> 00:33:54,948
SNAKE-BITE REMEDY.
THAT'S A GOOD ONE. ( chuckles )

78
00:33:58,451 --> 00:33:59,953
YES, IT WAS.

79
00:34:12,465 --> 00:34:16,469
Huck:
MEOW...MEOW!

80
00:34:21,474 --> 00:34:23,476
