81
00:34:30,984 --> 00:34:33,486
BETTER GET GOIN'. 
BEGINNIN' TO SMELL.

82
00:35:01,014 --> 00:35:03,516
WISH I KNOWED.
AWFUL SOLEMN, AIN'T IT?

83
00:35:09,773 --> 00:35:14,360
HECK, NO. HE'S DEAD.
HE AIN'T GOT NO USE FOR IT.

84
00:35:29,375 --> 00:35:31,377
( clanging )

85
00:35:40,887 --> 00:35:42,889
HOW COME THEY BURY
'EM SO DEEP?

86
00:35:43,890 --> 00:35:45,391
( Muff laughs )

87
00:36:01,407 --> 00:36:02,909
QUIET, YOU IDIOT.

88
00:36:06,412 --> 00:36:09,916
OH, YOU AIN'T GOT
NO FUN IN YOU NOWHERE.

89
00:36:14,921 --> 00:36:16,422
HERE. 
QUICKLY NOW, QUICKLY!

90
00:36:51,457 --> 00:36:52,959
DAMN IT!

91
00:36:56,963 --> 00:36:58,464
UGH!

92
00:37:07,473 --> 00:37:08,975
OH!

93
00:37:27,994 --> 00:37:30,997
YOU KILLED THE DOC, 
YOU DRUNKEN FOOL.

94
00:37:48,514 --> 00:37:49,515
SURE.

95
00:37:56,022 --> 00:37:58,524
( wind howling )

96
00:38:07,033 --> 00:38:09,035
IT WAS ME.
RAN INTO SOMETHIN'.

97
00:38:15,541 --> 00:38:19,545
IF DOC ROBINSON DIES, 
I RECKON HANGIN' WILL COME OF IT.

98
00:38:22,048 --> 00:38:24,550
( crash )

99
00:38:35,561 --> 00:38:37,563
LOOK WHAT I FOUND!

100
00:38:52,578 --> 00:38:54,580
ALL RIGHT,
IT'S A BLOOD PACT.

101
00:39:18,104 --> 00:39:20,606
"AND ROT."

102
00:39:26,112 --> 00:39:29,615
TOM'S BLOOD."

103
00:39:42,128 --> 00:39:44,630
( both gasp )

104
00:39:51,137 --> 00:39:53,139
( door creaks and slams )

105
00:40:31,677 --> 00:40:33,679
( door creaks and slams )

106
00:40:36,682 --> 00:40:39,185
( bell ringing )

107
00:41:18,224 --> 00:41:20,226
MORNIN', TOM.
MORNIN'.

108
00:42:48,314 --> 00:42:49,315
( loud crash )

109
00:43:05,331 --> 00:43:06,832
SPEAK UP.

110
00:43:13,339 --> 00:43:14,840
IT'S MY SLATE!

111
00:43:43,869 --> 00:43:46,372
HERE! CHICK, CHICK, CHICK,
CHICK, CHICK, CHICK, CHICK.

112
00:43:50,376 --> 00:43:51,877
HERE! CHICK, CH--

113
00:44:33,919 --> 00:44:34,920
YOU CAN'T.

114
00:44:36,922 --> 00:44:38,924
I'LL GET YOU SOME
OF THE REMEDY.

115
00:44:43,929 --> 00:44:45,931
( crickets chirping )

116
00:45:01,947 --> 00:45:02,948
MEOW!

117
00:45:05,451 --> 00:45:06,952
MEOW!

118
00:45:29,792 --> 00:45:31,794
BUT, HUCK--
WE DON'T SAY NOTHIN'.

119
00:46:05,327 --> 00:46:07,329
I MEAN, IN MY HEART.

120
00:46:14,837 --> 00:46:16,338
BUT YOU WAS DRUNK.

121
00:47:04,887 --> 00:47:06,889
I GOTTA GO.

122
00:47:08,390 --> 00:47:10,392
GOOD LUCK.
BYE, MUFF.

123
00:47:20,402 --> 00:47:21,403
WHICHEVER.

124
00:48:01,944 --> 00:48:04,947
( muttering )

125
00:48:18,460 --> 00:48:19,962
COULD IT HAVE BEEN
THAT VERY KNIFE?

126
00:48:22,965 --> 00:48:25,467
( muttering )

127
00:48:37,980 --> 00:48:40,983
HE WAS DRUNK, AS USUAL.
( all laugh )

128
00:49:06,508 --> 00:49:09,511
FROM DOC ROBINSON'S
POCKET.

129
00:49:34,036 --> 00:49:37,539
YOU COME UP HERE AND TELL US
EXACTLY WHAT YOU SAW.

130
00:49:42,044 --> 00:49:44,546
( panting )

131
00:50:12,074 --> 00:50:14,076
I...

132
00:50:27,089 --> 00:50:28,590
( laughing )

133
00:50:39,101 --> 00:50:40,602
THAT'S WHERE I LEFT IT 
WHEN I RAN AWAY.

134
00:50:55,117 --> 00:50:56,618
AND KNOCKED HIM OUT COLD.

135
00:51:06,559 --> 00:51:09,061
AND KNOCKED DOC ROBINSON
DOWN INTO THE GRAVE.

136
00:51:20,072 --> 00:51:21,574
I HEARD THE DOC SCREAM.

137
00:51:23,075 --> 00:51:25,077
( yelling and screaming )

138
00:51:28,080 --> 00:51:29,582
Man: AFTER HIM!

139
00:51:36,589 --> 00:51:37,590
Man 3: ME, TOO!

140
00:52:18,631 --> 00:52:20,132
I LIKE YOU.

141
00:53:34,206 --> 00:53:38,711
♪♪ I COULD FLY ♪♪

142
00:54:09,241 --> 00:54:14,747
♪♪ HOW COME? ♪♪

143
00:55:03,796 --> 00:55:06,298
I LOVE YOU.
NOW IT'S YOUR TURN.

144
00:55:07,299 --> 00:55:10,803
I, UH, I LOVE YOU.

145
00:55:14,306 --> 00:55:16,809
NOW ALL THAT'S LEFT
FOR US TO DO IS TO KISS.

146
00:55:39,331 --> 00:55:41,834
BUT EVEN IF I DID KNOW, 
I WOULDN'T TELL YOU!

147
00:55:53,345 --> 00:55:54,847
GIRLS.

148
00:56:07,209 --> 00:56:08,711
ARGH!
OOOH!

149
00:56:11,213 --> 00:56:14,216
( grunts and gasps )

150
00:56:45,247 --> 00:56:47,249
SO IF'N YOU WANNA COME...

151
00:56:49,251 --> 00:56:51,754
( sighs )

152
00:56:57,760 --> 00:57:00,262
AND MAKE US GRATEFUL
FOR EVERY BLESSING. AMEN.

153
00:57:10,773 --> 00:57:13,776
MARY! YOU COME BACK AND SIT
DOWN HERE THIS MINUTE.

154
00:57:51,814 --> 00:57:52,815
BEAST!

155
00:58:39,862 --> 00:58:41,864
MARY, DON'T
YOU DISOBEY ME, TOO.

156
00:59:30,412 --> 00:59:31,914
MAY GOD FORGIVE YOU.

157
01:00:37,479 --> 01:00:41,483
♪♪ OF EVERYONE
ELSE LIKE ME ♪♪

158
01:01:02,504 --> 01:01:07,509
♪♪ EXCEPT FOR THANKIN' ME ♪♪

159
01:01:37,539 --> 01:01:41,043
♪♪ THAT AIN'T HALF
WHAT I WOULD DO ♪♪

160
01:01:49,551 --> 01:01:52,054
♪♪ YOU ♪♪

