179
01:07:14,209 --> 01:07:18,213
PROBABLY.
I WISH I COULD DIE.

180
01:07:42,237 --> 01:07:43,738
I WISH THEY'D
CAUGHT HIM BY NOW.

181
01:08:22,777 --> 01:08:24,779
I'M FOR DRAGGIN'
THE RIVER.

182
01:08:29,284 --> 01:08:32,287
I'M SORRY.
I'M AFRAID HE'S RIGHT.

183
01:08:38,793 --> 01:08:41,296
GOOD NIGHT, MARY.
COME ON, BECKY.

184
01:08:49,804 --> 01:08:51,806
I DON'T KNOW, MA'AM,
I HOPE SO.

185
01:09:05,320 --> 01:09:06,321
OFF TO BED WITH YOU NOW.

186
01:09:44,859 --> 01:09:50,865
