( birds chirping )

189
01:10:49,924 --> 01:10:51,926
( loud explosion )

190
01:10:56,431 --> 01:10:58,433
( loud explosion )

191
01:11:17,952 --> 01:11:19,454
Man: FIRE!

192
01:11:29,464 --> 01:11:30,965
SOMEBODY MUST'VE DROWNED.

193
01:11:48,483 --> 01:11:49,484
Man: FIRE!

194
01:12:04,499 --> 01:12:07,001
YOU TAKE THIS SIDE.
I'LL TAKE THE OTHER.

195
01:12:47,542 --> 01:12:49,043
COME HERE!

196
01:12:56,551 --> 01:12:58,553
TOM!

197
01:13:04,559 --> 01:13:06,060
LOOK!

198
01:14:01,115 --> 01:14:04,118
BY THE HONORABLE JUDGE
CYRUS THATCHER.

199
01:14:36,651 --> 01:14:40,154
