ARE WE FOR THEIR LOSS.

200
01:15:17,191 --> 01:15:20,695
THAT WAS A MAGNANIMOUS
LIE HE TOLD.

201
01:15:56,731 --> 01:15:59,150
( sniffs )
( sobs )

202
01:16:09,243 --> 01:16:11,245
WE WILL REMEMBER YOU.

203
01:16:16,751 --> 01:16:18,252
IT'S A MIRACLE!

204
01:16:23,758 --> 01:16:24,759
TOM!

205
01:17:02,797 --> 01:17:04,298
HUCKLEBERRY.

206
01:17:14,308 --> 01:17:16,811
NONSENSE! YOU'RE
COMING WITH ME.

207
01:17:21,816 --> 01:17:22,817
Woman:
TOM...

208
01:17:47,341 --> 01:17:49,343
( guffaws )

209
01:17:55,850 --> 01:17:57,351
WHEN THEY EAT OUTDOORS.

210
01:18:19,874 --> 01:18:22,877
TAKE YOUR CAKE, YOUNG LADY. 
TIME WE GOT A MOVE ON.

211
01:18:27,882 --> 01:18:28,883
Aunt Polly: TOM!

212
01:18:36,390 --> 01:18:37,892
Aunt Polly:
YOU, TOM!

213
01:18:52,406 --> 01:18:54,408
NEVER YOU MIND.
JUST DO AS I SAY.

214
01:18:58,913 --> 01:18:59,914
ALL RIGHT.

215
01:19:11,926 --> 01:19:13,928
HAPPY FOURTH!

216
01:19:15,429 --> 01:19:19,433
( shouting, laughter )

217
01:19:57,471 --> 01:19:58,472
♪♪ ...SSOURI! ♪♪

218
01:20:30,504 --> 01:20:32,506
