01:21:23,057 --> 01:21:24,058
...SSOURI!

222
01:21:51,085 --> 01:21:52,086
♪♪ ...SSOURI! ♪♪

223
01:23:34,688 --> 01:23:45,199
♪♪ MO-SSOURI ♪♪

224
01:24:28,242 --> 01:24:30,244
STAY RIGHT THERE.
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

225
01:24:49,263 --> 01:24:51,265
I'M GONNA GO GET BECKY THATCHER
A DRINK OF WATER.

226
01:25:05,279 --> 01:25:06,780
OF COURSE I'M SURE.

227
01:25:20,794 --> 01:25:23,797
THAT'S NOTHIN'. 
WAIT TILL YOU SEE WHAT'S UP AHEAD.

228
01:25:37,811 --> 01:25:38,812
LOOK.

229
01:25:50,824 --> 01:25:52,326
( crowd exclaims )

230
01:25:57,331 --> 01:25:59,666
OH!
( laughs )

231
01:26:06,673 --> 01:26:08,175
HERE IT IS, BECKY.

232
01:26:13,680 --> 01:26:14,681
HERE.

233
01:26:29,196 --> 01:26:30,697
