234
01:26:35,702 --> 01:26:38,205
BECKY, COME ON!

235
01:26:51,718 --> 01:26:55,722
YOU'LL NEVER
GET OUT OF HERE ALIVE!

236
01:26:56,723 --> 01:26:57,724
