237
01:27:22,749 --> 01:27:24,751
TOM SAID SOMETHIN' ABOUT
AN UNDERGROUND SPRING.

238
01:27:34,761 --> 01:27:36,263
CAN YOU SHOW 'EM HOW TO GET THERE?
SURE.

239
01:28:03,290 --> 01:28:04,791
Huckleberry:
I FOUND A LANTERN!

240
01:28:09,296 --> 01:28:11,298
THEY CAN'T BE FAR AWAY.

241
01:28:12,299 --> 01:28:14,301
BECKY! TOM!
( echoing )

242
01:28:18,305 --> 01:28:20,807
HEAR THAT?
WE'RE HERE! ( echoing )

243
01:28:22,809 --> 01:28:24,811
SHH! INJUN JOE!

244
01:28:37,324 --> 01:28:39,326
IT'S INJUN JOE'S!

245
01:28:45,832 --> 01:28:47,334
WE'D BETTER
KEEP ON GOIN'.

246
01:28:50,837 --> 01:28:52,339
Becky:
AAH! ( echoing )

247
01:28:59,846 --> 01:29:01,348
COME ON.

