01:29:13,360 --> 01:29:15,862
Judge Thatcher:
BECKY! ( echo )

249
01:29:21,368 --> 01:29:22,869
UP HERE.

250
01:29:31,378 --> 01:29:32,879
DON'T LOOK DOWN, BECKY.

251
01:29:47,394 --> 01:29:49,396
DON'T CRY, BECKY.

252
01:29:54,401 --> 01:29:57,404
BECKY! TOM! ( echo )

253
01:30:02,909 --> 01:30:05,412
THEY'LL BE HERE IN NO TIME.
I JUST KNOW IT.

254
01:30:07,914 --> 01:30:09,416
Judge Thatcher: BECKY!

255
01:30:12,419 --> 01:30:14,421
I TOLD YOU, BECKY.
THEY'RE HERE!

256
01:30:17,924 --> 01:30:22,429
NOW I'VE GOT YOU, TOM SAWYER.
NOW YOU'RE DEAD!

257
01:30:28,935 --> 01:30:30,437
AAH!

258
01:30:36,943 --> 01:30:38,445
BULL'S-EYE.

259
01:30:39,446 --> 01:30:42,949
( organ music playing )

260
01:31:02,135 --> 01:31:03,136
THOMAS.

261
01:31:10,143 --> 01:31:11,645
NOT TO FOLLOW YOU
INTO THAT CAVE.

262
01:31:21,154 --> 01:31:23,657
BUT UNCOMMONLY HEROIC
THING YOU DID.

263
01:31:40,674 --> 01:31:43,176
OH, YES. BUT YES,
OF COURSE, POLLY.

264
01:31:56,189 --> 01:31:57,190
HUCK.

265
01:32:30,223 --> 01:32:32,225
TO DO EVERYTHING.

266
01:32:56,750 --> 01:33:00,253
ONE OF THESE DAYS
YOU GOTTA HAVE SOME RESPONSIBILITY!

267
01:33:02,255 --> 01:33:03,757
HMM.

268
01:33:08,261 --> 01:33:09,763
OLD JOHN.

269
01:33:16,269 --> 01:33:17,771
OH, TOM!

270
01:33:36,790 --> 01:33:39,292
WELL, THE WAY THINGS TURNED OUT, 
I RECKON I'LL HAVE TO.

271
01:33:52,806 --> 01:33:54,307
THANKS.
THANKS?

272
01:33:55,809 --> 01:33:57,310
FOR BEIN' MY FRIEND.

273
01:34:06,820 --> 01:34:12,325
THERE YOU ARE. THERE! AHA!
( laughs )

274
01:34:20,834 --> 01:34:22,836
AW, MUFF, 
YOU HAVEN'T CHANGED A BIT.

275
01:34:31,845 --> 01:34:33,346
COME ON, JOHN.

276
01:34:51,364 --> 01:34:53,366
( horn )

277
01:34:57,370 --> 01:35:00,373
( chattering )

278
01:35:13,386 --> 01:35:14,387
( laughs )

279
01:35:27,901 --> 01:35:29,402
( horn blares )

280
01:35:37,911 --> 01:35:39,913
GOOD-BYE, SIDNEY. 
GOOD-BYE.

281
01:35:57,931 --> 01:35:58,932
THANK YOU, TOM.

282
01:36:05,755 --> 01:36:06,756
I LOVE YOU, TOM.

283
01:36:07,757 --> 01:36:09,259
I LOVE YOU, AUNT POLLY.

284
01:36:14,264 --> 01:36:17,767
BYE.
BYE.

285
01:36:22,772 --> 01:36:25,275
BYE.
BYE.

286
01:36:39,789 --> 01:36:41,791
Mary:
BYE, TOM!

287
01:36:44,794 --> 01:36:46,296
Tom:
BYE!

288
01:37:05,815 --> 01:37:10,820
♪♪ AND THE BOY IS GONE ♪♪

289
01:38:02,872 --> 01:38:05,875
♪♪ FREE ♪♪

